quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,74,"“Uye rangarirai pavakakuitai vatevedzeri mushure memaAad (vanhu verudzi rwemaAad) uye vakakupai pekugara munyika, mukava munovaka dzimba mumabani, uye mukagadzira dzimba mumakomo. Naizvozvo rangarirai nyasha dzaAllah (makomborero aAllah), uye musave munotenderera muchikonzera huori panyika.”"
  7,75,"Vatungamiriri veavo vakanga vachizvitutumadza kubva muvanhu vake vakati kune avo vainge vasina simba, kune avo vaitenda: “Munozviziva here kuti Swaalih ave anotumwa naTenzi vake?” Vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, tinotenda muneizvo zvaakatumwa nazvo.”"
  7,76,"Avo vaizvitutumadza vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, hatitendi mune izvo zvamuri kutenda mazviri.”"
  7,77,"Naizvozvo vakave vanouraya ngamera hadzi iya, uye (nokuda kwekushaya hunhu) vakatyora mirairo yaTenzi vavo, uye vakati: “Iwe Swaalih! Chiunza izvo zvawaitivimbisa kana uri muzvirokwazvo mutumwa (hwaAllah).”"
  7,78,"Naizvozvo kundengendeka kwenyika kwakavabata, vakasiiwa vakatambarara vakapfugama mudzimba dzavo (misoro yavo yakatarisa pasi)"
  7,79,"Nokudaro (Swaalih) akavafuratira, uye akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Ndakave ndinosvitsa mashoko aTenzi vangu kwamuri, uye ndikakupai yambiro yakanaka asi hamudi vanoyambira zvakanaka.”"
  7,80,"Uye (rangarirai) Loti, paakati kuvanhu vake: “Munoita here chitadzo chakaipisisa chisina kumboitwa mushure menyu nani zvake pasi rose?”"
  7,81,"“Zvirokwazvo, munopedzera shungu dzenyu kuvarume (pabonde) muchisiya vakadzi. Saka muri vanhu vanodarikidza mwero.”"